                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseZero" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingZero" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p class="fst-italic">Andersonville National Historic Site is located in southwest Georgia. The park is approximately 12 miles north of Americus and 11 miles south of Montezuma on GA-49.</p>
                            </div>
